{"tid":1056934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應該好似一般情侶咁 抑或 有自己一套","createTime":"2019-03-11T14:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T15:05:10.000Z","uid":163524,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4839d490973692ffcaeb16090c1c45de85d9d1d","tid":1056934,"uid":163524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"我同我女朋友兩個都偏向鍾意自己思考<br />\n兩個都鍾意靜靜地 唔鍾意多人嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n相處方式同一般情侶好大分別<br />\n其他情侶會bb前bb後<br />\n每分每秒報到<br />\n你嗲吓我，我又嗲吓你<br />\n<br />\n相反，我同女朋友就好少呢啲<br />\n平時都係叫英文名多<br />\n又唔會成日報到、傾電話、messages<br />\n每日都會傾計就梗㗎啦<br />\n只係冇其他情侶咁多、咁癡纏<br />\n<br />\n我同佢應該喺平凡中搵到屬於我地、又冇衝突嘅相處方式<br />\n抑或<br />\n學其他情侶咁纏綿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我同女朋友都覺得冇乜問題，有自己共融嘅相處方式絕對唔出奇"},{"pid":"aba8b1bf7545873e1a42e154535514dff6d6e471","tid":1056934,"uid":163524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"拍拖都好少去玩<br />\n反而係去下weekend market/workshop etc<br />\n<br />\nFor reference: 我雙魚佢射手"},{"pid":"9dab4a27ee789e247f6acd2922c790332aadc998","tid":1056934,"uid":60727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:06:46.000Z","msg":"你自己都答咗自己"},{"pid":"40122178e1f5fdbd6cb24797a9d9f217057f9b33","tid":1056934,"uid":40766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:07:18.000Z","msg":"兩個相處得舒服就得啦"},{"pid":"d6b8c6e353eadcf6b8bf5e60a2ea2d8abe7f4179","tid":1056934,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"開心舒服咪得law, 都唔明做乜有啲人又要屈就自己又要覺得自己好偉大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95732de531ac7522476cb4e6a05434bde3d5573","tid":1056934,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:08:04.000Z","msg":"咁你有無帶套"},{"pid":"f92ed769ba99dc00695614f06417b431f0f3319a","tid":1056934,"uid":163524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"048170affbbee37260b6c20d68409dee4b0a345c","